Package: kindling
Type: Package
Title: Tidymodels Extension for Torch-Based Neural Networks
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Joshua", "Marie",
      email = "joshua.marie.k@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a higher-level interface to the 'torch' package for defining,
    training, and tuning neural networks within the 'tidymodels' ecosystem. Supports
    feedforward (multi-layer perceptron) and recurrent neural networks (RNN, LSTM, GRU)
    via 'parsnip' model specifications, reducing boilerplate code while enabling
    seamless integration with workflows, recipes, and tuning tools.
